√ renders with default props 
√ calls onSubmit with sanitized value on Enter key press
√ clears input value on Enter key press


Type of Testing: Unit Testing

#Key Test Cases:

Renders correctly with default props:Ensure that the Input component renders with default properties.

Calls onSubmit with sanitized value on Enter key press:Simulate pressing the Enter key and check if the onSubmit function is called with a sanitized value.
Clears input value on Enter key press:

Verify that the input value is cleared after pressing the Enter key.